---
import PageShell from "../../layouts/PageShell.astro";
---

<PageShell
  title="k1eu / work"
  description="Tomasz Kielar (k1eu) work — projects, client case, recommendations."
  ogUrl="https://k1eu.dev/work/"
  mainClass="gap-10"
>
  <section class="flex w-full flex-col gap-10 text-left">
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xl justify-start">
        <span class="glitch text-3xl font-semibold" data-text="work">work</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[var(--pink-dim)]">selected projects + client work.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[var(--pink-bright)]">projects</p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <li>
          <a class="neon-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/k1eu/later">Later</a>
          - Raycast menubar app for macOS.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="neon-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/k1eu/typed-formdata">
            TypedFormData
          </a>
          - Utility library for typed FormData in TypeScript.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            class="neon-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline"
            href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=k1eu.just-ts-snippets"
          >
            Just Typescript Snippets
          </a>
          - Bare-necessities JS/TS snippets for VS Code.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[var(--pink-bright)]">client case</p>
      <div class="space-y-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          <a
            class="neon-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline"
            href="https://apps.apple.com/pl/app/opti-ener/id6473692228"
          >
            OptiEner for Hewalex
          </a>
          - mobile app to control, monitor, and analyze smart-home energy usage.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--pink-dim)]">Built with React Native, Expo, TypeScript.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[var(--pink-bright)]">recommendations</p>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <li class="space-y-1">
          <div>
            <span class="text-[var(--pink-bright)]">Samuel Helm</span>
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--pink-dim)]">
              project manager, articulate entertainment
            </span>
          </div>
          <p>Led full-stack delivery with high quality and clear communication.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="space-y-1">
          <div>
            <span class="text-[var(--pink-bright)]">Haley Power</span>
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--pink-dim)]">
              brand + training specialist
            </span>
          </div>
          <p>Made mobile approvals smooth and guided the team with patience.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="space-y-1">
          <div>
            <span class="text-[var(--pink-bright)]">Rob Eifler</span>
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--pink-dim)]">cto at defined</span>
          </div>
          <p>Deep React expertise, turning complex UX into intuitive flows.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="space-y-1">
          <div>
            <span class="text-[var(--pink-bright)]">Peter Lancaster</span>
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--pink-dim)]">
              ceo at brandactif singapore pte.ltd
            </span>
          </div>
          <p>Delivered the Siri/Google Assistant app under tight deadlines.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="space-y-1">
          <div>
            <span class="text-[var(--pink-bright)]">Ludvig Sylvén</span>
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--pink-dim)]">
              head of product and business development
            </span>
          </div>
          <p>Proactive, curious, and consistently delivered on time.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--pink-dim)]">
        full recommendations on
        <a class="neon-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/k1eu">
          linkedin
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageShell>
